    48→ *                                 its rebalance future will be kept in the metadata if the
    49→ *                                 member has sent the join group request
    50→ * 2. Awaiting sync future: when the group is in the awaiting-sync state, its sync future
    51→ *                            is kept in metadata until the leader provides the group assignment
    52→ *                            and the group transitions to stable
    53→ */
